<br>
I say gives mages a whole line of charm summoned. Again probably useless overall, but necro's get plant only nukes and thats a limited use line.<br>
<br>
Necro's are the masters of undead, they charm undead, druids the master of nature, they charm animals. So why not let the masters of summoning charm summoned creatures. Hell I would mind putting points into that(a least compared to MGB and some of the other abilities).<br>
<br>
Being able to go into the hole and charm something and solo. I think that it would fit in with &quot;the vision&quot;.  Also, I think they need to increase the numbered of summoned creatures out there. If not, remove the whole damn summoned only nukes and give us cold nukes. <br>
<br>
Whatever, I'll keep dreaming. <p><p ALIGN=CENTER><a href="http://ddl.dyc.edu/~felix/tests/thug-life.htm" target="_blank"><img src="http://ddl.dyc.edu/~felix/tests/thug-life.jpg" alt="I am 3% thug-life"></a></p>
