<br>
But again, mages do not have *anything* that even supports that we should be able to charm.  It's like people ignore the druid/enchanter/necro spells before they realize why they get dire charm<br>
<br>
Necros *do* have normal undead charm, druids *have* animal charm and Enchanters have everything charm.  Mages have no summoned monster charm, and our summoned DDs are slower gained than druids (yeah its strange, go druids)<br>
<br>
