<br>
1.  Have pets *not* destroy no-drop items given to them by their owner until they are no longer pets (either charm breaks, or the owner goes LD or they die).<br>
<br>
2.  Implement a /pet give back command that has the pet return any weapons, etc. that it has been given.  This would enable pet classes who put the time/money into acquiring weapons with powerful effects to garner some advantage from it.<br>
-----<br>
<br>
Honestly, I think implementing #1 would be too difficult for charmed pets.  Perhaps even for all pets.  #2, however, would be very useful... and if it functioned for only tradeable items, it would not endanger the no-drop flag.  <br>
<br>
Personally, I'd still like to see a pet weilding Kriezen's Flame... but I suppose that will probably never happen. ;-) <p>
