<br>
The equipping of items would allow us to give them proc weapons, however a lot are level restricted above 49 unfortantely.  So Im not sure if that would actually do anything<br>
<br>
However I really like the idea of being able to get items back from pets, maybe through a vendor interface linked to a specific command.  VI has shown they can change how pets act with /pet hold.  If they introduce the bazaar coding, this could be a possiblity<br>
<br>
